{"tid":2501120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"狗咬貓事件｜柴犬咬死貓B第6日 男子揚言五區毒狗被捕","createTime":"2021-04-23T06:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T07:47:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"d233fe77ff3c22e8f57398f0e7b719fde657ab49","tid":2501120,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:59:46.000Z","msg":"灣仔會議展覽中心舉行的寵物節，周日發生「狗咬死貓」命案，一隻只有手板大的貓B疑遭路過的柴犬咬死，事件經過至今第六日有新發展，一名男子涉嫌「妨害公眾安寧」，被警方拘捕。據悉，被捕男子於事發後曾遷怒其他狗隻，竟在社交群組發出「死亡預告」，揚言在全港五區放置「毒朱古力餌」大報復。警方於下午3時將交代事件，《蘋果》屆時將進行直播。<br />\n<br />\n一連四日的寵物節由上周四（15日）開始，於灣仔會議展覽中心舉行，至昨日（18日）尾聲之際，竟發生「血案」。一隻只有手板大的貓B，疑遭路過的柴犬咬死，貓主於fb講述事件，稱涉事柴犬未有戴上口罩，更指控狗主一度稱「隻狗不嬲會咬貓」，事後不顧而去。狗主其後發帖，雖然承認所養狗隻咬貓並致歉，但細節卻與貓主說法有出入。警方早前指接獲報案，初時將案件暫列殘酷對待動物跟進，至今日拘捕狗主涉嫌「妨害公眾安寧」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210423/5ZT6CXVIIZGNNOCKDFAQTNYVPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210423%2F5ZT6CXVIIZGNNOCKDFAQTNYVPY%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=004c581a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210423%2F5ZT6CXVIIZGNNOCKDFAQTNYVPY%2F&h=ce936eac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210423/5ZT6CXVIIZGNNOCKDFAQTNYVPY/</a>"},{"pid":"66104d057cad8a73aa060942ca7d36731c6dff59","tid":2501120,"uid":41873,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">they are well paid for it. 大家唔洗吹奏班狗 </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e01a51c8ed0a340ab92f5f5e5d0ffdf3a89d8271","tid":2501120,"uid":65747,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:02:31.000Z","msg":"揚言在全港五區放置「毒朱古力餌」大報復。<br />\n<br />\n? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets